OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeatwaves likely to        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finfluence holiday choices -
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FTUI                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of TUI has said heatwaves and 
OL,6, climate change could prompt people to  
OL,7, take their holidays in spring or autumn
OL,8, and choose cooler destinations.        
OL,10,FSebastian Ebel, chief executive of the 
OL,11,Ftour firm, said holidaymakers might    
OL,12,Fchoose to travel to Greece in November,
OL,13,Fbenefiting the travel industry.        
OL,15,FDestinations such as the Belgian or    
OL,16,FPolish coast might become more popular,
OL,17,Fhe added.                              
OL,19,FTUI said July's wildfires in Rhodes had
OL,20,Fcost the firm 25m euros (#21.5m).      
